# Global Contract (SSOT v3.4)

## Non-negotiables
- meta-only: 본문/라인/로그 전문 출력 금지.
- Fail-Closed: 불확실/누락/에러는 반드시 exit 1 + reason_code.
- Output-based evidence only: 증빙은 표준 게이트 출력만 인정.
- 1 PR = 1 Purpose: 목적 혼합 금지.
- R4(.github/workflows/*)는 Single Lane: 동시에 1개 PR만 유지.

## Required sections for any PR prompt you generate
- Purpose
- Scope
- Invariants
- DoD (output-based)
- Negative test
- Failure modes + reason_codes
- Minimal diff plan
- References
